videos.description: Devonte' Graham gets a bounce pass to Mitch Lightfoot underneath the basket and Lightfoot finishes with the flush.
videos.headline: Graham sets up Lightfoot slam

videos.description: Udoka Azbuike elevates for the flush to extend Kansas' lead.
videos.headline: Azubuike makes easy dunk for Jayhawks

videos.description: Dean Wade misses a 3-pointer and Xavier Sneed swoops in for the putback dunk for Kansas State.
videos.headline: Wildcats answer with sweet putback dunk

videos.description: Sviatoslav Mykhailiuk makes the deep 3-pointer to tie the Jayhawks' game against the Wildcats before halftime.
videos.headline: Mykhailiuk hits 3-pointer at the buzzer for Kansas

videos.description: Udoka Azubuike works his way around the defense and finishes with the floater for the Jayhawks.
videos.headline: Azubuike beats the double team with hookshot

videos.description: Devonte' Graham gets a perfect pass to Udoka Azubuike who finishes with the slam for the Jayhawks.
videos.headline: Graham connects with Azubuike for alley-oop

videos.description: Dean Wade drives to the basket and sinks the jump shot to tie the game for the Wildcats against the Jayhawks.
videos.headline: Wade keeps Wildcats in it with turnaround jumper

videos.description: Cartier Diarra puts the Wildcats in the lead with a 3-pointer, also reaching 16 points in the second half against the Jayhawks.
videos.headline: Diarra stays hot for Wildcats with 3-pointer

videos.description: After Kansas scores, Barry Brown answers on the other end with an and-1 basket for the Wildcats.
videos.headline: Brown quiets Allen Fieldhouse with nice and-1 bucket

videos.description: Barry Brown misses a 3-pointer as the clock expires, sealing the win for Kansas.
videos.headline: Kansas avoids upset as Brown misses 3 at buzzer

videos.description: Devonte' Graham says his refocus at the half was key to him getting 23 points in Kansas' win over Kansas State.
videos.headline: Graham says win in rivalry game is huge for Kansas
